  "key_design_notes": [
    "MongoDbConnector.start() validates ALL config fields before accepting; stop() nulls config",
    "MongoDbConnector.validate() checks both field validation AND live connection (via validateConnection)",
    "MongoDbConnection.execute() is a retry-loop wrapper — retries on any Throwable via ErrorHandler",
    "MongoDbConnection.databaseNames() short-circuits when CaptureScope=DATABASE; collections() short-circuits when CaptureScope=COLLECTION",
    "ChangeStreamPipelineFactory.create() chains: sizePipeline → userAndInternalPipeline → splitPipeline",
    "CursorPipelineOrder controls INTERNAL_FIRST / USER_FIRST / USER_ONLY ordering in pipeline factory",
    "OversizeHandlingMode: FAIL (default) / SKIP (adds bsonSize filter) / SPLIT (adds $changeStreamSplitLargeEvent stage)",
    "FiltersMatchMode: REGEX uses $replaceRoot+namespace concat approach; LITERAL uses $in/$nin on ns fields directly",
    "MongoDbOffsetContext.getOffset() merges timestamp+order+resumeToken+txnId; stores incremental snapshot context when not in initial snapshot",
    "SourceInfo.Position stores BsonTimestamp + optional SessionTransactionId (lsid+txnNumber) + optional resumeToken string",
    "MongoDbConnectorConfig.ALL_FIELDS is a static Field.Set used for validation across connector and task"
  ],

